articularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/160163/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Apomorphine, Ropinirole, Opicapone, Cabergoline, Entacapone, Tolcapone, Rotigotine, Bromocriptine, Pergolide, Pramipexole, Amantadine, Levodopa', 1767369485);
